[ ] Create experimental framework (RepeatedStratifiedKFold)
    - Main Experiment Flow & Folds
        :: Parameters 
            - dataset_source - string 
            - dataset_name - string 
            - dataset_version - number
            - dataset_author - string 
            - task_type - string (classification | regression) 
            - model - string (e.g. MLPClassifier :: Default)
            - model_overrides  - object
            
        :: Classification
            - Dataset Information   
                - Types 
                    - Overall Info 
                    - Per-Fold Info
                - Overall Info 
                    - Train and Test Split Count 
                    - List of Labels 
                    - Frequencies of Labels
            - Performance Metrics 
                - Common Metrics 
                    - Accuracy Score 
                    - Balanced Accuracy Score
                    - Cohen's Kappa Score 
                    - Matthews Correlation Coefficient 
                    - Precision Score 
                    - Recall Score 
                    - F1 Score 
                    - PR-AUC Score 
                    - ROC-AUC Score
                    - Brier Loss & Brier Skill Score 
                    - Log Loss 
                    - Confusion Matrix 
                    - Training Time 
                    - Prediction Times  
                - Figures
                    - Calibration Curve 
                    - PR-AUC Curve 
                    - ROC-AUC Curve 
                    - Train / Test Loss Curve
                    - Train / Test Objective Function Curve
                    - Confusion Matrix Plot  
        :: Regression
            - Dataset Information   
                - Types 
                    - Overall Info 
                    - Per-Fold Info
                - Overall Info 
                    - Train and Test Split Count 
                    - Histogram of Labels (Deciles) 
                    - Deciles of Labels 
            - Performance Metrics 
                - MAE 
                - MedAE 
                - MSE 
                - RMSE
                - MAPE 
                - R2 
                - Explained Variance Score 
                - Residuals 
                    - Percentiles 
                    - Histogram 
            - Curve 
                - Histogram of Residuals 
                - Actual vs Predicted Graphs 
                
    - Reporters & Callbacks
        - JSON Reporter 
        - Text Reporter 
        - HTML Reporter 
    
